212
00:09:33.698 --> 00:09:34.782  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So...

213
00:09:34.866 --> 00:09:36.784  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
girls' weekend...

