00:09:52.092 --> 00:09:55.595  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Talk about boys,
complain about our families,

222
00:09:55.678 --> 00:09:57.431  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
