223
00:09:57.514 --> 00:09:59.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Okay, let's talk about boys.

224
00:09:59.849 --> 00:10:02.810  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
