225
00:10:02.894 --> 00:10:04.645  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Don't you just want to run your fingers

226
00:10:04.729 --> 00:10:05.980  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
