235
00:10:26.334 --> 00:10:29.003  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So...

236
00:10:29.087 --> 00:10:30.589  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What do you think?

237
00:10:30.671 --> 00:10:32.673  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
