238
00:10:32.757 --> 00:10:33.633  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
my favorite dress!

239
00:10:33.716 --> 00:10:34.842  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Don't worry.

240
00:10:34.926 --> 00:10:36.636  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You get to try on my clothes too.

241
00:10:36.719 --> 00:10:38.846  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I grabbed a pair of sweats from my hamper.

242
00:10:38.930 --> 00:10:41.475  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Heads up for the nacho cheese
on the thigh.

243
00:10:41.558 --> 00:10:43.268  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Oh!

244
00:10:43.351 --> 00:10:46.813  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
