245
00:10:46.896 --> 00:10:52.068  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Wait. There is one outfit
of yours that I wanted to try.

246
00:10:56.573 --> 00:10:57.824  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Harper?

247
00:10:57.907 --> 00:10:59.867  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Where'd you go?

248
00:10:59.951 --> 00:11:02.703  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Harper!

249
