255
00:11:16.801 --> 00:11:18.261  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We need to find Murray!

256
00:11:18.345 --> 00:11:19.846  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
