Look, I felt bad
about how things went yesterday,

266
00:11:53.963 --> 00:11:56.090  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
so I did some research on girl stuff,

267
00:11:56.174 --> 00:11:58.301  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
and I thought I'd give you a mani-pedi.

268
00:11:58.385 --> 00:12:02.889  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So come and sit in the chair...

269
00:12:02.972 --> 00:12:06.560  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
