00:19:01.223 --> 00:19:04.184  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
We need to help him, like Irona.

439
00:19:04.268 --> 00:19:05.519  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
When you are done here,

440
00:19:05.603 --> 00:19:09.732  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
you can go knock out
a couple loads of laundry.

441
00:19:09.816 --> 00:19:12.192  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Irona, why is Murray dusting?

442
00:19:12.276 --> 00:19:15.154  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I am a robot now, Master Richie.

443
00:19:15.237 --> 00:19:16.530  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What? Since when?

444
00:19:16.614 --> 00:19:18.365  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ever since I comforted him,

445
00:19:18.449 --> 00:19:20.701  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
he's been saying he's a robot
and doing all my chores.

446
00:19:20.785 --> 00:19:22.954  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Well, I'm glad this wacky turn of events

447
00:19:23.037 --> 00:19:25.414  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
found a happy, permanent solution.

448
00:19:25.498 --> 00:19:27.374  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Cheers to that!

449
00:19:27.458 --> 00:19:29.335  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'll take a cold lemonade.

450
00:19:29.418 --> 00:19:31.378  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Come on, chop-chop.

451
00:19:31.462 --> 00:19:33.339  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Wait. This makes sense now.

452
00:19:33.422 --> 00:19:35.382  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[both] It does?

453
00:19:35.466 --> 00:19:36.759  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
The penguins cared for Murray

454
00:19:36.843 --> 00:19:38.761  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
when he was stranded out in the cold,

455
00:19:38.845 --> 00:19:40.220  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
and he acted like a penguin.

456
00:19:40.304 --> 00:19:41.555  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
And when Irona cared for him

457
00:19:41.639 --> 00:19:43.808  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
when you traumatized him
by holding up that club,

458
00:19:43.891 --> 00:19:45.768  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
he started acting like a robot.

459
00:19:45.852 --> 00:19:47.770  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
So you're saying if we care for him

460
00:19:47.854 --> 00:19:49.522  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
through a traumatic experience,

461
00:19:49.605 --> 00:19:51.732  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
he will change back to normal?

462
00:19:51.816 --> 00:19:53.860  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Okay, let us not do that.

463
00:19:53.943 --> 00:19:56.403  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
- We are doing that.
- Fine.

464
00:19:56.487 --> 00:19:59.073  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You care for him. I'll create the trauma.

465
00:20:02.284 --> 00:20:03.410  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hello, Brittany?

466
00:20:03.494 --> 00:20:06.413  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Yeah, I can't make it
down to the boutique today,

467
00:20:06.497 --> 00:20:09.792  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
so will you put those handbags,
the tiara in the window,

468
00:20:09.876 --> 00:20:12.211  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
and the rest of the boutique
on Richie's tab?

469
00:20:12.294 --> 00:20:14.213  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Thanks, doll. [smooches]

470
00:20:14.296 --> 00:20:16.007  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
It's okay, Murray.

471
00:20:16.090 --> 00:20:17.842  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You're gonna be okay, buddy.

472
00:20:17.925 --> 00:20:20.386  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
It's working.
Keep pretending to order stuff.

473
00:20:20.469 --> 00:20:22.555  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Yeah, because I'm pretending.

474
00:20:24.098 --> 00:20:25.265  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Hello, Ricardo?

475
00:20:25.349 --> 00:20:27.018  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I can't make it
down to the dealership today,

476
00:20:27.101 --> 00:20:29.228  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
so can I just give you
Richie's credit card?

477
00:20:29.311 --> 00:20:32.439  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Stop! Darcy, stop wasting Richie's money!

478
00:20:32.523 --> 00:20:35.109  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Murray, you're back!

479
00:20:35.193 --> 00:20:36.360  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I missed you, dude.

480
00:20:36.443 --> 00:20:37.820  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Thanks for saving me, Richie.

481
00:20:37.904 --> 00:20:41.157  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Now allow me to save you
millions of dollars.

482
00:20:43.659 --> 00:20:47.038  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ha! There.

483
00:20:47.121 --> 00:20:49.082  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
