489
00:21:03.137 --> 00:21:06.933  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ Which requires Murray to kick rocks ♪

490
00:21:07.016 --> 00:21:10.061  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ I need them, they're simply divine ♪

491
00:21:10.144 --> 00:21:12.646  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
