492
00:21:12.730 --> 00:21:15.858  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ Murray's better as a penguin ♪

493
00:21:15.942 --> 00:21:20.362  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
♪ I'd even take him as a robot ♪

494
00:21:21.572 --> 00:21:23.449  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Just stop, Darcy.

495
00:21:23.532 --> 00:21:25.785  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Okay, fine.


